ro.isdc.wro.manager.callback
Interface LifecycleCallback

All Known Implementing Classes:
LifecycleCallbackDecorator, LifecycleCallbackRegistry, LifecycleCallbackSupport, PerformanceLoggerCallback
public interface LifecycleCallback

Defines callbacks invoked by the manager during processing. Any of the lifecycle method can throw a RuntimeException which will be handled properly by LifecycleCallbackRegistry.

Since:
1.4.3
Author:
Alex Objelean
